Persona Builder ← CRM Import → Persona Library
                                               ↓
Competitive Snapshot → Gap Map
                       ↓
Knowledge Base ← Third-Party Voice → Proprietary Index
                       ↓
                 ACTIVE CONTEXT SESSION
```

